title: Newly appointed Chinese envoy calls on FM Jilani
content:
ISLAMABAD, Sep 28 (APP):Newly-appointed Chinese Ambassador Jiang Zaidong called on Caretaker Foreign Minister Jalil Abbas Jilani here on Thursday.
During the meeting they discussed bilateral cooperation in multiple domains including China Pakistan Economic Corridor (CPEC).
The two sides expressed their firm resolve to further strengthen the all-weather strategic cooperative partnership between Pakistan and China.
